metadata.name: ASTROKID DF #1
metadata.description: Astrokid-DF aka The Golden Astrokid, is the very first designer figure release from the TEENSONACID, founder of the Acidverse. The Golden Astrokid was first designed to commemorate the AKUltra collection surpassing 100ETH traded volume across all markets. Now available in physical form featuring 3 variations with a supply of just 100 units. Produced with the help of Potluck Protocol the Golden Astrokid celebrates the first 12 months of the Acidverse brand and the community built upon the vision provided by Potluck Protocol
